詹姆斯·布朗特回忆达蒙·阿尔本不想与他在《乔尔斯·荷兰》中合影https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-blunt-recalls-damon-albarn-not-wanting-to-be-photographed-with-him-for-jools-holland-3533867?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=詹姆斯·布朗特回忆达蒙·阿尔巴恩不想为乔尔斯·荷兰与他合影Liberty DunworthWed, 08 Nov 2023 10:24:31 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3533867 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他还回忆了诺埃尔·加拉格尔对他的批评</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-blunt-recalls-damon-albarn-not-wanting-to-be-photographed-with-him-for-jools-holland-3533867">詹姆斯·布朗特 (James Blunt) 回忆起达蒙·阿尔本 (Damon Albarn) 不想在《Jools Holland》中与他合影的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-blunt">詹姆斯·布朗特 (James Blunt)</a>回忆起达蒙·阿尔本<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/damon-albarn">(Damon Albarn)</a>不想在《后来……与乔尔斯·霍兰》 <em>(Later…With Jools Holland)</em>的一集中与他合影。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/james-blunt-soundtrack-of-my-life-3071561">詹姆斯·布朗特：“小精灵是我一直想成为的摇滚明星”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这个话题是在演员凯西·伯克 (Kathy Burke) 在她的播客系列<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/a-little-bo-ock-with-james-blunt/id1654059310?i=1000633085002" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Where There&#39;s A Will, There&#39;s A Wake》</em></a>的一集讨论中出现的。这位创作型歌手回忆起<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a>主唱对他的“回避”。</p><p>伯克回忆起对布朗特的新回忆录<em>《松散地基于一个编造的故事》</em>中的其中一个段落感到“有点恼火”，伯克向艺术家询问了他在“<em>后来……与乔尔斯·霍兰德”</em>节目中讨论他的出场的段落——即一个时刻那是在镜头外发生的。</p><p> “他们最后给所有乐队拍了一张集体照……是达蒙·阿尔本拒绝出现在照片中还是不想让你出现在照片中？”她问。</p><p> “我不太清楚。我确信他是一个可爱的小伙子，但他不想让我出现在这一集的照片中，”布朗特回答道。</p><p> “每个人都拿到了照片，照片被贴在朱尔斯·霍兰德工作室的墙上，”布朗特补充道。 “出于某种原因，他不想让我出现在照片中，所以他们拍那张照片时我被关在更衣室里。然后他离开了，然后他们让我出去拍第二张照片，但我的照片不一定挂在墙上。” </p><figure id="attachment_3533888" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3533888" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3533888" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt1@2000x1270.jpg" alt="詹姆斯·布朗特于 2023 年 9 月 16 日在维多利亚公园参加 BBC Radio 2 In The Park 2023 表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt1@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt1@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt1@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt1@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt1@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt1@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3533888" class="wp-caption-text">詹姆斯·布朗特于 2023 年 9 月 16 日在维多利亚公园举行的 BBC Radio 2 In The Park 2023 节目中表演。图片来源：Luke Brennan/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>后来在播客节目中，布朗特开玩笑地回忆起 2006 年<em>NME</em>授予他最差专辑奖的那一刻，并表示他希望那份出版物刊登他的讣告。</p><p>当被问及目前的护柩者是谁时，布朗特接着说他希望<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">加拉格尔</a>兄弟入伍。他承认了另一个关于他听说过的关于他自己的狡猾谣言。</p><p> “[我会选择]那些加拉格尔兄弟，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔</a>，他叫什么名字，他们很乐意这样做。我认为他们已经签约了，”他开始说道，同时也提到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>和 Blur 多年来竞争的讽刺。</p><p> “确实如此，他们都对我和我的音乐表示了很好的支持，所以让他们成为节目的一部分真是太好了，”他补充道。 “我确实在不同的地方遇到过诺埃尔。我认为他只是在别人背后说这些话。因为在你看来，他是个胆小鬼。” </p><figure id="attachment_3533886" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3533886" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3533886" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt@2000x1270.jpg" alt="James Blunt performs during a Gala Dinner at Somerset House ahead of the Laver Cup at The O2 Arena on September 22, 2022" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3533886" class="wp-caption-text"> James Blunt performs during a Gala Dinner at Somerset House ahead of the Laver Cup at The O2 Arena on September 22, 2022. CREDIT: Clive Brunskill/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Here the host chimed in to ask if it was true that Noel once claimed that he was moving out of Ibiza because Blunt had just moved there. Blunt responded: “Yeah, he said he couldn&#39;t have me writing my shitty songs just down the road from him. And it was really weird, when he left, house prices just rocketed.”</p><p> The singer also made headlines with the anecdotes shared in his memoir last month when he recalled how he <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-blunt-on-living-with-carrie-fisher-she-became-my-best-best-friend-3519024">developed a close relationship with actor Carrie Fisher</a> .</p><p> According to the singer, he moved in with the <em>Star Wars</em> icon in 2003 when he went to LA to further his career and would always “go into her room to talk, no matter if it was 11pm or 3am”.</p><p> He added that living with Fisher meant that “she became my best, best friend”.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-blunt-recalls-damon-albarn-not-wanting-to-be-photographed-with-him-for-jools-holland-3533867">James Blunt recalls Damon Albarn not wanting to be photographed with him for &#39;Jools Holland&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
